          </div>
          <div class="grid__item large--one-half large--right medium--one-half medium--right text-wrapper">
            <h3>The Magic is in the numbers</h3>
            <p>Graduated compression works by slowly changing its strength (measured in mmHg) over the length of the sock or sleeve. Take a couple quick measurements and we maximize its effictiveness by fine tuning this process to your body.</p>
            <p><span>No measuring tape?</span> We can help you measure with a dollar bill and a pair of headphones.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
